  "title": "Talent Acquisition Manager - MEDICAL (West/GOVT) - up to $7.5k #HAO",
  "description": "<p>Salary: up to $7500 </p><p>Working Days & Hours: Mon-Fri Office Hours</p><p>Location: Queenstown</p><p>Job Description:</p><p>Lead and manage a\nteam of 8, providing guidance, mentorship, and performance management.</p><p>\nCo develop and implement strategic talent acquisition plans to meet the\norganization's hiring needs.</p><p>\nEnsure operational excellence in all recruitment processes and procedures.</p><p>\nStay abreast of industry trends and best practices in talent acquisition,\ncontinuously improving our recruitment strategies.</p><p>\nAnalyze recruitment metrics and provide regular reports to senior management.</p><p>\nFoster relationships with stakeholders (internal and external) including hiring\nmanagers, agencies, educational institutes, etc.</p><p>Job Requirements: Min Degree in Human Resources or similar w min 5 yrs of relevant large volume recruitment experience, preferably in Healthcare industry</p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Ally Audrey Lok Xin Woon</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R21102307</p><p><a href=\"mailto:allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</a><a href=\"mailto:allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"mailto:allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
